Subject: [PATCH 3/7] feat: add IndexReconciler for Primary/Secondary index
 diff (Part 2)

Implements adaptive lexical-prefix reconciliation at the document Id grain.
IndexReconciler executes an IndexQueryPlan against both search clients
concurrently, diffs the resulting Id sets, and writes a report.
Includes IndexReconcilerTests and RECONCILIATION-DESIGN.md.

